title: Kyle Mooney | More Shocking Jan. 6 Texts Reveal GOP Lawmakers Planning Coup Attempt: A Closer Look
description:
Seth takes a closer look at the investigation of the January 6 insurrection and Trump's attempted coup now implicating several members of Congress as more shocking text messages emerge.

Then, Kyle Mooney talks about his show All Star Hits, reminisces on watching VHS tapes with friends after SNL after-parties and dives deep into a bag of old tapes with Seth.
